message: "If you use this dataset or code, please cite it as below."
type: dataset
title: "Supplementary Material: Large Language Models in Scrum Management: Findings from an International Survey of Practitioners"
abstract: "This repository contains the analysis scripts, survey dataset, codebooks, and pre-generated reports for the research paper investigating how Agile practitioners use LLMs (AI chat assistants such as ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini) to support Scrum management activities. The study is based on an international survey of 159 practitioners from 37 countries, including 81 active LLM users, providing insights into usage patterns, perceived benefits, challenges, and future perspectives."
